 m/<wbr />routes/54955439</a><u></u><u></u></p><p>The RWGPS route uses Pedri
 ck Road to avoid the Stevenson Bridge closure\, but it might be worth a cal
 l to Solano County Department of Resource Management about possible use of 
 Stevenson Bridge on weekends.<u></u><u></u></p><p>The plan is to start from
  Westlake Shopping Center at 8:30 a.m. and bike in a 46 mile counter-clockw
 ise loop to Chepo’s Tamales in Elmira.<u></u><u></u></p><p>More details bel
 ow. Please let me know if you need additional information or have suggestio
 ns for route improvements.<u></u><u></u></p><p>Thanks\,<u></u><u></u></p><p
