 cond Saturday – May 9\, 2026<u></u><u></u></li><li>Start time: <b>8:30</b> 
 a.m.<u></u><u></u></li><li>Start location: Westlake Shopping Center\; 1260 
 Lake Boulevard\, Davis.<u></u><u></u></li><li>Distance: 46 miles\, flat.<u>
 </u><u></u></li><li>Contact: Anne Huber\; <a href="mailto:anneh@dcn.org" ta
 rget="_blank">anneh@dcn.org</a>\; 916-206-2922<u></u><u></u></li><li>Servic
 es (Food\, water\, bathrooms): Chepo’s Tamales in Elmira<u></u><u></u></li>
 <li>No need to RSVP<u></u><u></u></li><li>Rain cancellation or postponement
 : communicated via the listserv.<u></u><u></u></li><li>Pace: 14 - 17 mph wi
 th regroups. The speed is meant to be an indicator of speed on flat terrain
