 g to regroup. There might be some stopping for scenery.<u></u><u></u></li><
 li>Route: <a href="https://ridewithgps.com/routes/54955439" target="_blank"
 >https://ridewithgps.com/<wbr />routes/54955439</a><u></u><u></u></li></ul>
 <p><u></u> <u></u></p><ul><li>For general information about the second Satu
 rday ride and bicycling with the Davis Bike Club\, please see: <a href="htt
