DESCRIPTION:Davis Art Studio Tour Preview Exhibit  \nStudio Tour: May 16-17\, 10 AM – 5 PM (free) \n  \nThis year’s Davis Art Studio Tour returns\, and is open the weekend of May 16-17 for art lovers to enjoy for free! Stroll through 40+ art studios in Davis\, learn more about artists’ work\, and support our local creatives by buying directly from them.  \n  \nThe Pence will preview one piece per artist in the exhibit\, and you can plan your tour through the display! Art in various media is on display\, including glass\, wood\, paintings\, photography\, ceramics\, mixed media\, and more.  \n  \nLearn more about the studio tour: https://www.davisopenstudios.com/ \n  \nImage: Cathie James-Robinson\, “My Happy Place”
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/davis-art-studio-tour-preview-exhibit/2026-05-17/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Cathie-James-Robinson-My-Happy-Place-copy.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencesocialmedia@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
